flegn zey epes fregn fragn? flegt ir zey dertseyln vos ir hot adurkhgemakht in tsayt fun der milkhome?

00:10:41.785 --> 00:10:43.483
zey- zeyer veynik.

00:10:44.468 --> 00:10:48.498
tsufelik, s'iz do ki- tsum bayshpil, ikh hob a khaver n- in Amerike

00:10:48.498 --> 00:10:50.698
vos b- ikh bin geganen mit im tsuzamen in di shule

00:10:51.066 --> 00:10:55.129
zey, er hot oykh tsvey tekhter. zayne tsvey tekhter hobn gevolt visn ales

00:10:55.129 --> 00:10:56.662
vos er hot, fun di lagern.

00:10:56.989 --> 00:11:00.881
mayne tsvey tekhter, mir, me redt a mol, ober zey zoln zayn interesirt

00:11:01.900 --> 00:11:03.328
spetsyel nisht.

00:11:03.672 --> 00:11:06.163
me flegt zey tsu dertseyln epizodn.

00:11:06.405 --> 00:11:09.841
ober azoy zol zayn mamesh interesirt vegn dem

00:11:10.084 --> 00:11:10.972
leyder.

00:11:10.928 --> 00:11:13.487
ver flegt mer dertseyln, ir oder ayer froy?

00:11:14.860 --> 00:11:15.951
UNK

00:11:15.012 --> 00:11:16.592
ikh denk az es s-

00:11:16.817 --> 00:11:18.937
s'iz kimat di zelbe zakh, s'iz nisht

00:11:19.450 --> 00:11:22.717
un ir mit ayer froy tsuzamen flegt ir redn vegn dem?

00:11:22.707 --> 00:11:24.408
mir flegn a sakh redn vegn dem,

00:11:24.408 --> 00:11:26.412
zi flegt mir dertseyln fun ir zayt

00:11:26.487 --> 00:11:28.624
vayl in di lagern hob ikh ⟨dokh zi⟩ nisht gekent.

00:11:28.967 --> 00:11:31.757
⟨undz⟩ beyde flegn mir dertseyln di gantse geshikhte fun

00:11:31.757 --> 00:11:35.154
⟨zayt ikh bin⟩ avekgeshikt fun Skarzhisk nokh BERGEN BELSEN.

00:11:35.920 --> 00:11:36.895
mit undz

00:11:36.895 --> 00:11:41.178
nor fun Tshenstokhov hot men zey geshikt nokh BERGEN BELSEN. undz hot men geshikt nokh BUCHENWALD.

00:11:41.472 --> 00:11:45.940
zi flegt mir dertseyln di gantse, vi azoy zey hobn zikh geratevet oyf di ban

00:11:45.940 --> 00:11:49.312
vi azoy me hot bombardirt di ban un di, di ale zakhn.

00:11:50.382 --> 00:11:53.939
mir flegn zikh dertseyln avade fun Skarzhisk, avade, vayl

00:11:53.939 --> 00:11:57.531
zi hot mir UNK nakher, m'hot tsuzamengeredt, hot zi gezogt az ken, dort gekent mayn tatn.

00:11:58.633 --> 00:11:59.808
farshteyt ⟨ale⟩

00:11:58.920 --> 00:12:03.335
iz in tsvey un zibetsikstn yor kumt ir keyn Yisroel?

00:12:02.310 --> 00:12:03.290
keyn Yisroel.

00:12:03.527 --> 00:12:05.293
vos geshet do in Yisroel?

00:12:05.333 --> 00:12:07.470
in Yisroel, me zukht arbet.

00:12:08.050 --> 00:12:09.630
mir

00:12:09.687 --> 00:12:13.832
m'hot gekoyft, koydem kol hot men f- gekoyft di dire, dos iz di ershte dire vos me hot gekoyft

