m'hot gemakht SWEATERS dortn.

00:12:29.402 --> 00:12:33.846
ober di b- fabrik hot zikh likvidirt, un ikh hob tsurik ongehoybn zukhn mayn arbet.

00:12:34.088 --> 00:12:36.866
azoy ikh hob tsurik ongehoybn arbetn bay mayn fakh.

00:12:37.024 --> 00:12:38.739
s'iz davke nisht geven shlekht.

00:12:39.943 --> 00:12:43.227
un biz s'hot zikh di, biz mayn froy iz krank gevorn.

