un zi iz mamesh geshtorbn fun dem, fun di lagern, vos zi hot gehat di krankeyt.

00:13:03.754 --> 00:13:04.822
fun di lungen.

00:13:04.822 --> 00:13:07.620
vayl zi hot, di lungen zenen gevorn, hobn oyfgehert arbetn in gantsn.

00:13:07.620 --> 00:13:10.104
zi hot gelebt di gantse tsayt nokh di bafrayung

00:13:10.104 --> 00:13:11.916
mit finef un draysik protsent lungen.

00:13:13.828 --> 00:13:15.357
azoy hot mir der dokter gezogt.

00:13:15.853 --> 00:13:18.263
zi hot gekent geyn keyn shtign. zi hot nisht gekent

00:13:18.263 --> 00:13:19.579
di mindste sh-

00:13:19.579 --> 00:13:21.500
shver, hot zi nisht gehat keyn otem.

00:13:21.507 --> 00:13:25.654
ober ikh hob zi prubirt opts- optsuhitn vifl ikh hob gekent, un azoy hot men

00:13:25.654 --> 00:13:28.571
