00:13:28.948 --> 00:13:31.270
biz zi hot shoyn nisht mer gekent

00:13:31.294 --> 00:13:32.671
s'hot zi nisht gearbet di lungen.

00:13:33.218 --> 00:13:36.283
vos hot pasirt tsu ayere tekhter do in land?

00:13:36.762 --> 00:13:38.792
di tekhter hobn ongehoybn tsu geyn in di shule

00:13:38.792 --> 00:13:40.097
geendikt di shule

00:13:40.693 --> 00:13:42.408
un nakher hobn zey khasene gehat

00:13:42.465 --> 00:13:45.170
eyne hot, hot khasene gehat mit eynem velekher

00:13:45.170 --> 00:13:47.285
zenen, iz er aroysgeforn nokh Italye

00:13:47.680 --> 00:13:49.990
vi heyst di eyne vos zi hot khasene gehat?

00:13:49.850 --> 00:13:52.200
SARA, SARA. SARA ⟨PASAL⟩.

00:13:50.800 --> 00:13:51.670
SARA.

