do iz zey geganen zeyer, zeyer shlekht. zey hobn

00:14:00.307 --> 00:14:04.953
er hot gearbet als, hot a gutn, tsufelik a gutn kop. keyn geendikter iz er nisht.

00:14:05.247 --> 00:14:08.025
ober er hot a kop far g- far BUSINESS.

00:14:08.250 --> 00:14:14.305
hot gearbet do, a b- a gehilf in a ⟨GAR⟩, azoy az er, s- s'hot, zey hobn nisht gekent ekzistirn, zenen gevezn t-

00:14:14.305 --> 00:14:15.483
dray kinder.

00:14:15.574 --> 00:14:20.073
zey hobn bashlosn tsu forn nokh Italye. der foter hot gehandlt mit ⟨SHTICHIM⟩.

00:14:20.383 --> 00:14:25.355
nakher hot mayn eydem ongehoybn epes, langzam ongehoybn mit UNK.

00:14:26.037 --> 00:14:30.908
un, er hot zikh dortn, hot dortn ESTABLISHED di, di BUSINESS in MILANO.

00:14:31.065 --> 00:14:33.460
iz geyt im davke ze- ⟨shlekht⟩.

00:14:33.006 --> 00:14:34.890
dos iz di gresere tokhter.

00:14:33.990 --> 00:14:36.695
di greste. di yingere tokhter hot a-

