vi heyst zi?

00:14:37.005 --> 00:14:38.669
TSIPI. TSIPORA.

00:14:39.216 --> 00:14:42.098
zi hot khasene gehat davke mit a ⟨YisroelIM⟩ do mit a s-

00:14:42.098 --> 00:14:45.690
er iz oykh kimat, er iz geboyrn, dakht zikh mir in AFGHANISTAN.

00:14:46.253 --> 00:14:50.077
ober gekumen er iz alt geven a yor tsayt, azoy az k- me ken makhn az er

00:14:51.096 --> 00:14:55.106
zi iz geganen oyf SHIRUT LEUMI oyfn GOLAN in a MOSHAV.

00:14:55.517 --> 00:14:58.784
UNK ⟨MAGSHIMIM⟩. zi hot dortn bakent mit a bokher.

00:14:59.078 --> 00:15:01.552
er shtudirt davke do in RECHOVOT.

00:15:02.436 --> 00:15:04.729
der UNK gevezn a yor tsayt kimat.

00:15:04.729 --> 00:15:07.529
ober zi iz gevezn, hot gegebn SHIRUT LEUMI dortn oyfn

00:15:07.650 --> 00:15:12.622
ALSO zey hobn zikh bakent un azoy, m'hot bashlosn khasene tsu hobn un dortn blaybn oyfn GOLAN.

00:15:12.932 --> 00:15:14.431
un azoy bizn hayntikn tog.

00:15:14.431 --> 00:15:15.795
zey hobn finef kinder.

00:15:16.442 --> 00:15:20.070
di tokhter in GOLAN hot finef kinder, un di tokhter in MILANO?

00:15:19.360 --> 00:15:20.370
hot dray kinder.

00:15:21.212 --> 00:15:23.342
iz hot ir tsuzamen akht eyniklekh.

00:15:23.985 --> 00:15:26.375
un azoy, azoy iz geblibn.

00:15:26.652 --> 00:15:29.582
m'iz sh- dos lebn iz nisht azoy laykht dortn oyfn GOLAN

00:15:30.027 --> 00:15:34.189
un materyelish, ⟨di groyse tokhter⟩ iz, iz gut, es geyt gut.

00:15:34.347 --> 00:15:36.180
s'kimat me ken zogn a raykher mentsh.

00:15:36.473 --> 00:15:38.458
ober di oyfn GOLAN iz s-

00:15:39.004 --> 00:15:41.259
s'iz shver. zey makhn a lebn. zey

00:15:41.603 --> 00:15:44.418
s'iz parnose do, ober zey z- arbetn zey beyde zeyer shver.

00:15:44.843 --> 00:15:49.427
ir hot farbindungen mit di kinder, mit di eyniklekh? me treft zikh, me zet zikh?

00:15:46.560 --> 00:15:48.740
yo, keseyder, keseyder.

00:15:49.483 --> 00:15:53.864
mit di trefn, mitn trefn iz a bisl nisht azoy oft.

00:15:53.905 --> 00:15:55.704
tsum bayshpil mit di groyse

00:15:56.082 --> 00:15:57.713
zi kumt tsvey mol in yor.

00:15:58.022 --> 00:16:00.176
peysekh tsayt kumt zi oyf tsvey vokhn

00:16:00.267 --> 00:16:02.775
un yetst kumt zi oyf fir vokhn. yetst iz zi do in land.

00:16:04.266 --> 00:16:08.495
un f- dos zet men zikh azoy yedn vokh tsvey dray mol in di vokh.

00:16:08.670 --> 00:16:12.612
mit di groy- klenere zet men zikh tsvey dray mol in yor.

00:16:13.243 --> 00:16:16.156
vayle tsu forn iz, me vert nisht yinger.

00:16:16.365 --> 00:16:17.844
un s'iz zeyer vayt.

00:16:18.070 --> 00:16:20.038
ober mir redn etlekhe mol oyf di vokh.

00:16:20.078 --> 00:16:21.219
keseyder in farbindung.

00:16:21.428 --> 00:16:25.584
a sakh mol kumen zey bay a tsufal, tsum bayshpil, zi vil zikh zen mit di andere shvester

00:16:25.584 --> 00:16:30.720
oder zi kumt tsu mir un, oder kumt tsu zey, un a- tomer kumt tsu mir, ze ikh zikh nokh a mol mit zey.

00:16:30.726 --> 00:16:32.258
ober azoy az

00:16:32.258 --> 00:16:34.450
nisht mer vi tsvey dray mol durkh di.

00:16:34.843 --> 00:16:38.000
ikh hob aykh gevolt nokh fregn a frage.

00:16:38.413 --> 00:16:39.863
nokh dem

00:16:39.863 --> 00:16:44.593
alemen vos ir hot mir dertseylt, nokh dem shvern iberlebn, nokh di ale tsores

00:16:44.593 --> 00:16:46.363
vos ir hot adurkhgemakht

00:16:47.314 --> 00:16:50.801
kukndik tsurik vos alts iz adurkh

00:16:51.516 --> 00:16:53.636
ikh volt aykh gevolt fregn

